    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那这个x轴的类别具体怎么安排？我看你提到\"many categories\"，大概需要几个？还有那个很长的Lorem ipsum文本是要作为其中一个类别标签吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "x-axis",
        "category1",
        "category3",
        "category4",
        "category6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，x轴要7个类别，从category1到category7。其中第二个类别故意用那段很长的Lorem ipsum文本——\"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, qui minim labore adipisicing minim sint cillum sint consectetur cupidatat\"——用来测试长文本在图表中的显示效果。x轴标题写\"this is x axis\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "x-axis",
        "category1",
        "category3",
        "category4",
        "category5",
        "category6",
        "category7",
        "adipisicing",
        "cupidatat",
        "consectetur"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，x轴已经设置好了，7个类别包括那段长文本。现在y轴怎么定？范围和标签有要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "y-axis",
        "yaxisText"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "y轴范围设10到150，标签用yaxisText。然后加一个柱状图系列，叫\"sample bar\"，数据是[52, 96, 35, 10, 87, 34, 67, 99]——等等，我刚发现数据有8个值，但x轴只有7个类别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "y-axis",
        "bar",
        "sample bar"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确实，数据点和类别数量不匹配。我需要调整一下——把最后一个数据点99去掉，变成7个值[52, 96, 35, 10, 87, 34, 67]，这样就和7个类别一一对应了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bar",
        "sample bar",
        "category1",
        "category7"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样数据就对应上了。那个长类别标签的显示没问题吧？要确保\"adipisicing\"和\"cupidatat\"这些词都能完整显示。",
